.block-reviews
    .container-small
        h2.block-reviews__title.title Отзывы
        .slider-default.swiper
            .slider-default__wrapper.swiper-wrapper
                +loop(8)
                    .component-slide.swiper-slide
                        a(href="https://youtu.be/QwHhxnv6BYo" data-video-id="QwHhxnv6BYo").component-slide__link.js-modal-video
                        .component-slide__image
                            +icon('play')
                            img(src=require('../../public/images/block-built__slide.jpg'))
                        p.component-slide__title Антонио Бандерас
            .block-built__buttons
                .block-built__pagination.slider-default__pagination.swiper-pagination
                a(href="#").btn.btn--primary смотреть все отзывы